@CompanyEmployeeApp_HostAddress = http://localhost:5297

### Get all companies
GET {{CompanyEmployeeApp_HostAddress}}/api/companies
Accept: application/json

### Get company by id
GET {{CompanyEmployeeApp_HostAddress}}/api/companies/1
Accept: application/json

### Get employees of company 1
GET {{CompanyEmployeeApp_HostAddress}}/api/companies/1/employees
Accept: application/json

### Create company
POST {{CompanyEmployeeApp_HostAddress}}/api/companies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "NewCo",
  "address": "789 Startup Lane"
}

### Get all employees
GET {{CompanyEmployeeApp_HostAddress}}/api/employees
Accept: application/json

### Get employee with details (OOP composition)
GET {{CompanyEmployeeApp_HostAddress}}/api/employees/1/details
Accept: application/json

### OOP polymorphism demo - GetDisplayInfo() for each employee
GET {{CompanyEmployeeApp_HostAddress}}/api/employees/entity-demo
Accept: application/json

### Create employee
POST {{CompanyEmployeeApp_HostAddress}}/api/employees
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Alice",
  "lastName": "Brown",
  "salary": 52000,
  "companyId": 1
}

### Add details to employee
POST {{CompanyEmployeeApp_HostAddress}}/api/employees/details
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "employeeId": 3,
  "email": "bob@globalsoft.com",
  "phone": "555-0199",
  "department": "Sales",
  "joinDate": "2024-01-15"
}
